  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Phase 3 study is intended to demonstrate superiority of either Sotagliflozin high dose
      or low dose versus placebo on glycosylated hemoglobin A1C (A1C) reduction at Week 24 when
      used as an adjunct in adult patients with type 1 diabetes mellitus (T1D) who have inadequate
      glycemic control with insulin therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
